{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotation","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation."}]}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob